@startuml
title Application Startup

actor JVM
participant VulnadoApplication
database Postgres
participant SpringApplication

JVM -> VulnadoApplication: main(args)
note right: Entry point of the application

VulnadoApplication -> Postgres: setup()
note right: Initialize database schema and seed data

Postgres -> Postgres: connection()
note right: Establish database connection

Postgres -> Postgres: insertUser(username, password)
note right: Insert seed users into database

Postgres -> Postgres: insertComment(username, body)
note right: Insert seed comments into database

VulnadoApplication -> SpringApplication: run(VulnadoApplication.class, args)
note right: Start Spring Boot application

SpringApplication -> SpringApplication: initialize application context
note right: Spring Boot initializes application context and beans

alt Database operations fail
    Postgres -> VulnadoApplication: Print exception and exit application
    note right: Application terminates on database setup failure
end
@enduml